<H3> <TI>   BP, British Gas Consider Joint Exploration </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    BP, British Gas Consider Joint Exploration </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM0605120294 London THE GUARDIAN in English 6 May 94 p 
17--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PM0605120294 </F>
