<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Trade Balance With EU Continues To Be Positive </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR0605144094 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1145 GMT 6 
May 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR0605144094 </F>
