<F P=100> FRANCE </F>
<H3> <TI>   Juppe Rules Out Participation in Haitian Operation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Juppe Rules Out Participation in Haitian Operation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR1305120094 Paris LIBERATION in French 13 May 94 p 12 </F>
<F P=103> BR1305120094 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris LIBERATION </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] France is "certainly not" prepared to participate in 
a military intervention in Haiti, [Foreign Minister] Alain Juppe 
declared in Washington yesterday. He also reiterated Paris' 
"irreversible" condemnation of the "military regime which has 
usurped power." The United States has threatened a military 
operation in Haiti. 

</TEXT>

