<F P=106> [Report signed "jan": "Interest Rates Are Going Down: </F>
National Bank Cuts Key Rates"] 
  [Excerpt] The downward trend of interest rates is 
continuing: As of next Friday [13 May], the Austrian National 
Bank will cut both the discount rate and the Lombard rate by 
0.25 percentage points to 5.5 and 4.5 percent respectively. The 
interest rate that is decisive for open market transactions 
(Gomex) will be reduced from 5.2 to 5.1 percent. [passage 
omitted] 

