<H3> <TI>   Hunt for Alien Submarine Continues </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Hunt for Alien Submarine Continues </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1305161594 Stockholm Radio Sweden in Swedish 1030 GMT 13 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1305161594 </F>
<F P=104>  Stockholm Radio Sweden </F>
<F P=105>  Swedish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Swedish Navy today continues its hunt for what 
is described as an alien submarine in the Gryt archipelago. Owe 
Wagermark, the defense staff's information chief, told us that 
the intensity of the hunt is as great as earlier this week and 
that the search continues unabated. The Navy has indications of 
alien underwater activity, and ships and helicopters are taking 
part in the search. 

</TEXT>

