  [Text] Foreign Minister Alekos Mikhailidhis met today with 
the German parliamentary delegation that is visiting Cyprus at 
the invitation of the Cypriot House of Representatives. The 
foreign minister briefed the German deputies on the latest 
developments in the Cyprus issue. They exchanged views on 
Cyprus' progress in joining the European Union [EU] and 
discussed Cypriot-German relations. Earlier, the delegation met 
acting President Alexis Galanos. 
