interest in a Cyprus solution will continue. In another 
statement, he said he is heading a German Bundestag initiative 
to put pressure on the German Government to influence Ankara so 
that it will take a conciliatory stance on the Cyprus issue. 
The initiative also advocates speeding up the procedure for 
Cyprus joining the EU. 

